ğŸš€ QUICK START (Choose One)
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

OPTION 1: SYMPHONY (Recommended - Beautiful & Easy)
$ bash ~/setup-symphony-screensaver.sh
$ hyprctl reload
$ pkill hypridle && sleep 1 && hypridle &
Time: 2 minutes


OPTION 2: OMARCHY (Flexible - Multi-Terminal)
$ bash ~/setup-omarchy-screensaver.sh
$ hyprctl reload
$ pkill hypridle && sleep 1 && hypridle &
Time: 5 minutes


OPTION 3: BOTH (Maximum Options)
$ bash ~/setup-symphony-screensaver.sh
$ bash ~/setup-omarchy-screensaver.sh
$ hyprctl reload
$ pkill hypridle && sleep 1 && hypridle &
Time: 10 minutes


