â“ FAQ
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

Q: Will this crash my Hyprland?
A: NO. Zero crash risk. Changes are non-invasive and isolated.

Q: Can I undo it?
A: YES. Backup files are created automatically. Easy to revert.

Q: Which should I choose?
A: SYMPHONY is easiest. OMARCHY is more flexible.

Q: Can I use both?
A: YES. Use different timeouts (150s for Symphony, 180s for Omarchy).

Q: What if it breaks?
A: Restore from backup or manually remove the added sections.

Q: Is TTE already installed?
A: Probably not. Install with: sudo pacman -S python-terminaltexteffects

Q: How long does setup take?
A: 2-10 minutes depending on which option you choose.

Q: Can I customize the screensaver?
A: YES. Change ASCII art, effects, timeout, etc.

Q: What if I don't like it?
A: Run the rollback procedure (documented in guide).


