âš¡ ULTRA QUICK (Copy-Paste)
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

Symphony (one command):
  bash ~/setup-symphony-screensaver.sh && hyprctl reload && \
  pkill hypridle && sleep 1 && hypridle &

Omarchy (one command):
  bash ~/setup-omarchy-screensaver.sh && hyprctl reload && \
  pkill hypridle && sleep 1 && hypridle &

Then wait 2.5 minutes or test: screensaver-launch


ğŸ¯ RECOMMENDED FLOW
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

1. READ: SCREENSAVER_SETUP_GUIDE.md (5 min overview)

2. VERIFY: Dependencies installed
   which tte && which jq && which alacritty

3. CHOOSE: Symphony or Omarchy (or both)

4. SETUP: Run the script for your choice

5. RELOAD: Hyprland and hypridle

6. TEST: Wait or manually trigger

7. CUSTOMIZE: (optional) Edit as desired

8. ENJOY: Your new screensaver!


ğŸ“ TROUBLESHOOTING
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

"TTE not found"
â†’ sudo pacman -S python-terminaltexteffects

"Screensaver doesn't trigger"
â†’ pkill hypridle && sleep 1 && hypridle &

"Screensaver doesn't exit on key press"
â†’ Press key again or reload Hyprland (Super+Shift+R)

"Window is small, not fullscreen"
â†’ Verify window rule in WindowRules.conf and reload

"Can't find script"
â†’ For Symphony: ~/.config/hypr/scripts/screensaver-launch
   For Omarchy: ~/.local/bin/screensaver-launch


ğŸš¨ EMERGENCY UNDO
â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

If something goes wrong:

Option 1 (Recommended):
  cp ~/.config/hypr/hypridle.conf.backup.* ~/.config/hypr/hypridle.conf
  cp ~/.config/hypr/UserConfigs/WindowRules.conf.backup.* \
     ~/.config/hypr/UserConfigs/WindowRules.conf
  hyprctl reload

Option 2 (Emergency):
  hyprctl reload (This reloads the actual config from disk)

Option 3 (Ultimate):
  Super+Shift+R or Ctrl+Alt+Backspace


